  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators of the study want to investigate the complex interactions between glucose
      metabolism, food intake/weight loss, and different appetite regulating hormones after ESG in
      comparison with conventional laparoscopic sleeve gastrectomy (LSG).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
